snippet.title: Teahouse of Souls - Official Trailer | Upload VR Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
Teahouse of Souls is a VR adventure game where players will have tea with souls in order to comfort them before they truly rest in peace. Explore memories, have conversations, and most importantly make tea for the souls in need of rest. Teahouse of Souls launches this year for Meta Quest, PICO, and Steam VR.

#GameTrailers #VR #SummerofGaming
